§0Some have heard the§0
§0rumor that Tom now§0
§0calls himself§0
§0'Herobrine', a mythical§0
§0creature who haunts§0
§0his diamonds, diamonds§0
§0which were cruelly§0
§0snatched before him...§0
§0there have been§0
§0reports
#- of §0

#- Tom, or 'Herobrine', in§0
