§0Surely he is of kind§0
§0heart? Neigh, may he§0
§0be of evil thoughts§0
§0and wick'd intentions.§0
§0Surely one can trust§0
§0someone who carries §0

#- only food? May he be§0
§0carring a weapon in§0
§0suclusion, anticipating§0
§0the right moment to§0
§0strike. Surely he can§0
§0be a friend? Neigh,§0
§0best beware the§0
§0Pearls of Ender that§0
§0may be hidden away in§0
§0thy inventory! Dost§0
§0believe that this§0
